n%20the%20city%20in%20a%20small%20car%2C%20climb%20electric%20poles...He%20said%20that%20I%20would%20bring%20clean%20politics.%20After%20that%2C%20the%20biggest%20scam%20in%20Delhi--the%20liquor%20scam%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%2C%20was%20done%20by%20his%20party%2C%20his%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bawana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20drink%20dirty%20water%20but%20Kejriwal%20-ji%20lives%20in%20a%20'sheeshmahal'.%20He%20lives%20in%20a%20house%20worth%20crores%20of%20rupees.%20He%20drinks%20clean%20water%20and%20gives%20you%20false%20statements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20bizarre%20claim%20has%20drawn%20fire%20from%20the%20BJP%20as%20well%20as%20theb%20Election%20Commission.%20The%20latter%20has%20demanded%20that%20he%20backs%20up%20his%20claim%20with%20evidence%20and%20warned%20that%20such%20comments%20that%20can%20cause%20rifts%20between%20the%20people%20and%20a%20breach%20of%20peace%2C%20are%20a%20punishable%20offence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20%26quot%3Bmixing%20poison%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20city's%20water%20supply%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20chaos...%20hoping%20the%20blame%20will%20fall%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20party's%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Delhi%20get%20drinking%20water%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh...%20but%20the%20Haryana%20government%20has%20mixed%20poison%20in%20the%20water%20coming%20to%20Delhi%20from%20the%20Yamuna%20and%20sent%20it%20here...%20it%20is%20only%20due%20to%20the%20vigilance%20of%20our%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%20engineers%20that%20this%20water%20was%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2057-second%20video%20shared%20widely%20online%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20seen%20at%20the%20bank%20of%20Yamuna%2C%C2%A0%20spl