st-arvind-kejriwal-for-yamuna-poisoning-claims-7586406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Haryana%20government%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20former%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20over%20his%20%26quot%3BYamuna%20poisoning%26quot%3B%20charge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-to-file-case-against-arvind-kejriwal-for-yamuna-poisoning-claims-7586406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Woman%2C%2029%2C%20Dies%20After%20Chiropractor%20%26quot%3BCracked%20Her%20Neck%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWeeks%20after%20experiencing%20neck%20pain%20during%20a%20gym%20workout%2C%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20reported%20feeling%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrack%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20neck%20died%20following%20chiropractic%20treatment%2C%20an%20inquest%20heard.%C2%A0After%20injuring%20her%20neck%20during%20a%20gym%20session%20in%20September%202021%2C%2029-year-old%20Joanna%20Kowalczyk%20declined%20a%20hospital%20procedure%20and%20opted%20for%20chiropractic%20therapy%20after%20researching%20alternative%20treatments.%20It%20is%20believed%20she%20suffered%20an%20arterial%20dissection%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20gym%20injury%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.com%2Fuk%2Fhealthcare%2Farticle%2Fgym-enthusiast-died-after-chiropractor-cracked-her-neck-mm6z5js96%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20month%20after%20suffering%20acute%20arterial%20dissections%2C%20Ms%20Kowalczyk%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20experienced%20further%20tears%20in%20the%20same%20area%20following%20a%20chiropractic%20neck%20adjustment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20inquest%20revealed%20that%20Ms%20Kowalczyk%20had%20an%20undiagnosed%20connective%20tissue%20disorder%2C%20which%20made%20her%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20arterial%20dissections-rare%20but%20potentially%20fatal%20tears%20in%20an%20artery's%20lining.%20She%20also%20had%20a%20history%20of%20migraines%20and%20joint%20hypermobility%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeila%20Benyounes%2C%20assistant%20coroner%20for%20Gateshead%20and%20South%20Tyneside%2C%20concluded%20that%20Ms%20Kowalczyk's%20death%20on%20October%2019%2C%202021%2C%20was%20caused%20by%20%26quot%3Ba%20combination%20of%20the%20consequences%20of%20chiropractic%20treatment%20following%20a%20naturally%20occurring%20medical%20event.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublishing%20her%20findings%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20coroner%20recommended%20that%20the%20General%20Chiropractic%20Council%20introduce%20guidelines%20requiring%20chiropractors%20to%20review%20a%20patient's%20medical%20history%20before%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChiropractic%20Treatment%20Followed%20Hospital%20Visit%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kowalczyk%20had%20initially%20gone%20to%20the%20hospital%20after%20hearing%20a%20crack%20in%20her%20neck.%20A%20CT%20scan%20was%20performed%2C%20and%20doctors%20advised%20her%20to%20undergo%20a%20lumbar%20puncture%20to%20rule%20out%20a%20possible%20haemorrhage.%20However%2C%20she%20discharged%20herself%20against%20medical%20advice%20and%20instead%20sought%20treatment%20from%20a%20chiropractor%20for%20pain%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inquest%20heard%20that%20she%20informed%20the%20chiropractor%20about%20her%20recent%20hospital%20visit%20and%20CT%20scan%2C%20but%20the%20chiropractor%20did%20not%20request%20any%20medical%20records%20before%20proceeding%20with%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20four%20weeks%2C%20Ms%20Kowalczyk%20underwent%20multiple%20chiropractic%20sessions.%20During%20an%20appointment%20on%20October%2016%2C%202021%2C%20she%20suddenly%20experienced%20severe%20dizziness%2C%20double%20vision%2C%20and%20tingling%20in%20her%20right%20hand%20and%20foot.%20She%20also%20had%20difficulty%20speaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chiropractor%20advised%20her%20to%20seek%20medical%20attention%2C%20but%20she%20did%20not%20go%20to%20the%20hospital%20immediately.%20Later%20that%20day%2C%20paramedics%20treated%20her%20at%20home%20and%2C%20after%20being%20told%20that%20dizziness%20and%20migraines%20were%20common%20after%20chiropractic%20adjustments%2C%20diagnosed%20her%20with%20a%20migraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inquest%20was%20told%20that%20the%20attending%20medical%20professional%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20aware%20that%20stroke%20symptoms%20can%20sometimes%20subside%20temporarily.%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Kowalczyk%20was%20eventually%20taken%20to%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20Hospital%20in%20Gateshead%2C%20where%20she%20died%20three%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoroner%20Issues%20Prevention%20of%20Future%20Deaths%20Report%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coroner%20formally%20recorded%20Ms%20Kowalczyk's%20death%20as%20a%20hospital%20death%20but%20issued%20a%20prevention%20of%20future%20deaths%20report%20to%20the%20North%20East%20Ambulance%20Service%20and%20the%20General%20Chiropractic%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBenyounes%20expressed%20concern%20that%20the%20chiropractor%20had%20not%20considered%20obtaining%20Ms%20Kowalczyk's%20medical%20records%20before%20treatment%2C%20despite%20knowing%20about%20her%20recent%20hospital%20visit%20and%20medical%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20noted%20that%20even%20an%20updated%20consent%20form%20from%20the%20British%20Chiropractic%20Association%20lacked%20a%20prompt%20for%20chiropractors%20to%20request%20medical%20records%20before%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20concerned%20that%20consideration%20to%20obtaining%20medical%20records%20should%20always%20be%20given%20before%20assessment%2C%20particularly%20where%20recent%20medical%20treatment%20or%20investigations%20have%20been%20undertaken%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20coroner%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organizations%20involved%20have%2056%20days%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20coroner's%20recommendations.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738158360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fith7q4ro_chiropractor_625x300_29_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-29-dies-after-chiropractor-cracked-her-neck-7588386%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Kowalczyk%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20experienced%20further%20tears%20in%20the%20same%20area%20following%20a%20chiropractic%20neck%20adjustment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2230%20Dead%2C%2060%20Injured%20In%20Maha%20Kumbh%20Stampede%2C%20Says%20UP%20Top%20Cop%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThirty%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20stampede%20that%20happened%20just%20before%20dawn%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20venue%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj%2C%20the%20police%20chief%20that%20oversees%20security%20at%20the%20massive%20religious%20gathering%20told%20reporters%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-five%20bodies%20have%20been%20identified%2C%20police%20officer%20Vaibhav%20Krishna%20told%20reporters%2C%20adding%2060%20were%20injured.%20Many%20have%20been%20hospitalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20casualties%20came%20hours%20after%20local%20reports%20and%20Prayagraj%20residents%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20about%20deaths%20at%20the%20stampede.%20The%20reports%20were%2C%20however%2C%20not%20consistent%20with%20the%20number%20of%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pre-dawn%20stampede%20at%20the%20Sangam%20area%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20broke%20out%20after%20many%20pilgrims%20jostled%20for%20space%20to%20take%20a%20holy%20dip%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Mauni%20Amavasya%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20auspicious%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20started%20breaking%20barricades%20before%20the%20stampede%20happened%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarojini%2C%20a%20Karnataka%20resident%20who%20came%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20came%20in%20a%20batch%20of%2060%20people%20in%20two%20buses.%20There%20were%20nine%20people%20in%20our%20group.%20Suddenly%20there%20was%20pushing%20in%20the%20crowd%2C%20and%20we%20got%20trapped.%20Many%20fell%20down%20and%20the%20crowd%20became%20uncontrollable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20at%20a%20local%20hospital%2C%20whose%20child%20was%20injured%2C%20said%20there%20was%20nowhere%20to%20go%20when%20people%20started%20pushing%20in%20the%20massive%20crowd.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20who%20pushed%20us%20were%20laughing%20while%20we%20begged%20them%20for%20kindness%20towards%20the%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Krishna%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Inspector%20in%20General%20(DIG)%20of%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20said%20the%20situation%20is%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Akhara%20Parishad%2C%20Mahant%20Ravindra%20Puri%2C%20who%20was%20headed%20towards%20the%20Triveni%20Sangam%20for%20the%20amrit%20snan%20said%20thousands%20of%20saints%20and%20Naga%20sadhus%20were%20coming%20with%20him.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20for%20the%20amrit%20snan...%20We%20will%20vacate%20the%20ghats%20very%20quickly%20so%20that%20all%20the%20devotees%20who%20have%20come%20here%20are%20able%20to%20take%20a%20holy%20dip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigambar%20Naga%20Baba%20Chidanand%20Puri%20of%20Panchayati%20Niranjani%20Akhara%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20after%20taking%20amrit%20snan%20that%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20people%20from%20the%20Niranjani%20Akhara%20are%20coming%20in%20small%20numbers%20to%20take%20the%20holy%20dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738158060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F07ghfglo_maha-kumbh-ani-_650x400_29_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F30-dead-in-stampede-at-maha-kumbh-before-mass-holy-dip-on-mauni-amavasya-7588061%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thirty%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20stampede%20that%20happened%20just%20before%20dawn%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20venue%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj%2C%20the%20police%20chief%20that%20oversees%20security%20at%20the%20massive%20religious%20gathering%20told%20reporters%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2230%20dead%2C%2060%20injured%20in%20Maha%20Kumbh%20stampede%20in%20Prayagraj%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738157952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117691568%2Cimgsize-1255733.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F30-dead-60-injured-in-maha-kumbh-stampede-in-prayagraj%2Farticleshow%2F117691302.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Helpline%20number%3A%201920%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F30-dead-60-injured-in-maha-kumbh-stampede-in-prayagraj%2Farticleshow%2F117691302.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20How%20India%20Can%20Deal%20With%20Trump%20And%20His%20Tariffs%20'Creatively'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EColombian%20President%20Gustavo%20Petro%20became%20the%20first%20major%20casualty%20of%20Trump%202.0's%20no-nonsense%20approach%E2%80%94some%20might%20argue%2C%20his%20unchecked%20ire.%20The%20US%20President%20wasted%20no%20time%20in%20showing%20the%20world%20that%20his%20recent%20fiery%20rhetoric%20wasn't%20just%20for%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Columbian%20President%20tried%20to%20go%20toe-to-toe%20with%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20man.%20First%2C%20Petro%20made%20a%20show%20of%20defiance%2C%20refusing%20to%20allow%20US%20military%20planes%20carrying%20illegal%20Colombian%20immigrants%20to%20land%20on%20his%20turf.%20He%20even%20lobbed%20a%20couple%20of%20undiplomatic%20words%20at%20him%2C%20calling%20Trump%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwhite-slaver%E2%80%9D%20allegedly%20bent%20on%20%E2%80%9Cwiping%20out%20the%20human%20species%E2%80%9D.%20Subtlety%20was%20clearly%20missing.%20And%20when%20Trump%20fired%20back%20with%20a%20threat%20of%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Colombian%20goods%2C%20Petro%2C%20trying%20to%20punch%20above%20his%20weight%2C%20promised%20to%20counter%20with%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENational%20Hero%20To%20Humiliation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20so%20good.%20But%20just%20hours%20after%20posting%20his%20defiant%20salvos%20on%20X%2C%20Petro%20folded%20faster%20than%20anyone%20could%20imagine.%20To%20everyone's%20surprise%2C%20he%20agreed%20to%20take%20back%20his%20undocumented%20citizens%E2%80%94on%20US%20terms.%20That%20meant%20they%20would%20be%20sent%20on%20military%20planes%2C%20shackled%20and%20handcuffed.%20If%20you%20are%20feeling%20charitable%2C%20you%20might%20spin%20this%20as%20both%20sides%20%E2%80%9Creaching%20a%20resolution%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20Petro%20got%20steamrolled.%20He%20went%20from%20being%20a%20national%20hero%20to%20national%20humiliation%20in%20record%20time.%20One%20moment%2C%20he%20was%20the%20fearless%20leader%20standing%20up%20to%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20country%3B%20the%20next%2C%20he%20was%20the%20guy%20who%20caved%20in%2C%20leaving%20his%20critics%20and%20supporters%20alike%20cringing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lesson%20is%20that%20going%20toe-to-toe%20with%20Trump%20may%20create%20a%20good%20spectacle%2C%20but%20in%20practice%2C%20it%20might%20just%20leave%20you%20wounded%20and%20scarred.%20%C2%A0At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20fiery%20spectacle%2C%20a%20smug%20White%20House%20issued%20what%20can%20only%20be%20described%20as%20a%20global%20warning%20with%20menace%3A%20%E2%80%9CToday's%20events%20make%20clear%20to%20the%20world%20that%20America%20is%20respected%20again.%E2%80%9D%20The%20message%20was%20that%20if%20you%20crossed%20Trump%2C%20you%20might%20just%20find%20yourself%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20his%20%E2%80%9CAmerica%20First%E2%80%9D%20doctrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Tremendous%20Tariff-Makers'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20wasted%20no%20time%20flexing%20his%20muscles%20either.%20He%20has%20been%20openly%20critical%20of%20India.%20Barely%20a%20week%20into%20his%20second%20term%2C%20he%20lumped%20India%2C%20China%20and%20Brazil%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctremendous%20tariff-makers%E2%80%9D%20club%E2%80%94essentially%20rebranding%20his%20friends%20and%20foes%20from%20the%20first%20term%20into%20a%20single%20category%20of%20troublemakers.%20The%20man%20who%20once%20rolled%20out%20the%20red%20carpet%20for%20%E2%80%9CHowdy%2C%20Modi!%E2%80%9D%20now%20seems%20more%20inclined%20to%20roll%20out%20the%20tariff%20charts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20while%20he's%20been%20busy%20berating%20EU%20countries%20and%20throwing%20shade%20at%20NATO%2C%20one%20country%20remains%20conspicuously%20untouched%3A%20Britain.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20went%20out%20of%20his%20way%20to%20heap%20praise%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%E2%80%94for%20reasons%20no%20one%20seems%20able%20to%20pinpoint.%20What's%20next%3F%20One%20wonders%20why%20the%20same%20generosity%20of%20spirit%20couldn't%20extend%20to%20India%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20spectacle%20of%20mutual%20adoration%20during%20Modi's%20US%20visits%20in%20his%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20unpredictable%20style%20and%20transactional%20worldview%20seem%20poised%20to%20complicate%20Washington's%20relationship%20with%20New%20Delhi.%20There%20is%20no%20re-election%20bid%20this%20time%20to%20temper%20the%20impulses%20of%20an%20unfiltered%2C%20unrestrained%20Trump.%C2%A0%20If%20his%20recent%20moves%20are%20any%20indication%2C%20his%20second%20term%20might%20see%20less%20fanfare%20and%20more%20hardball.%20And%20for%20India%2C%20navigating%20these%20waters%20may%20require%20more%20than%20just%20charm%20and%20photo%20ops%E2%80%94it'll%20demand%20some%20serious%20diplomatic%20footwork.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'America%20First'%20vs%20'Make%20In%20India'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Trump%20has%20made%20%E2%80%9CAmerica%20First%E2%80%9D%20his%20battle%20cry%2C%20India%20has%20long%20sworn%20by%20its%20own%20foreign%20policy%20doctrine%E2%80%94strategic%20autonomy.%20A%20doctrine%20that%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20allows%20New%20Delhi%20to%20chart%20its%20own%20course%20without%20bending%20to%20external%20pressures.%20But%20theory%20and%20reality%2C%20as%20history%20reminds%20us%2C%20don't%20always%20shake%20hands.%20Since%20COVID-19%2C%20nations%E2%80%94including%20India%E2%80%94have%20doubled%20down%20on%20domestic%20markets%2C%20expanded%20production%20bases%20and%20vowed%20to%20build%20supply%20chains%20as%20resilient%20as%20their%20political%20speeches%20claim%20them%20to%20be.%20But%20now%2C%20the%20world%20is%20faced%20with%20a%20resurgent%20America%20under%20Trump%202.0%2C%20whose%20zero%20tolerance%20for%20global%20balancing%20acts%20is%20well%20documented.%20Will%20India%20hold%20its%20ground%2C%20or%20will%20the%20weight%20of%20tariffs%2C%20trade%20imbalances%20and%20immigration%20disputes%20force%20it%20to%20%E2%80%9Cadjust%E2%80%9D%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20A%20'Tariff%20King'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20not%20forget%2C%20Trump%20has%20previously%20described%20India%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctariff%20king%E2%80%9D%2C%20highlighting%20what%20he%20viewed%20as%20excessively%20high%20import%20duties%20on%20US%20products.%20Examples%20of%20high%20tariffs%2C%20furnished%20by%20the%20US%20side%20to%20back%20their%20complaints%2C%20are%20as%20follows%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgriculture%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20tariffs%20on%20almonds%20(17%25)%20and%20apples%20(70%25)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuxury%20goods%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India's%20150%25%20tariff%20on%20imported%20alcoholic%20beverages%20like%20bourbon%20whiskey%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETechnology%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%20imposes%20high%20duties%20on%20high-end%20electronic%20goods%2C%20such%20as%20iPhones%20and%20laptops%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-end%20motorcycles%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20has%20imposed%20tariffs%20as%20high%20as%20100%25%20on%20luxury%20motorcycles%2C%20including%20those%20from%20Harley-Davidson%E2%80%94a%20frequent%20talking%20point%20for%20Trump%20in%20his%20first%20term%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedical%20Devices%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia's%20price%20caps%20on%20imported%20medical%20devices%2C%20like%20stents%2C%20have%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20US%20manufacturers%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20could%20push%20for%20sweeping%20tariff%20reductions%20or%20reciprocal%20measures.%20He%20may%20also%20threaten%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20on%20Indian%20exports%20if%20there's%20no%20progress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EClues%20From%20Trump%201.0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrade%20relations%20under%20Trump's%20first%20term%20were%2C%20at%20best%2C%20a%20mixed%20bag.%20While%20bilateral%20trade%20grew%2C%20tensions%20over%20tariffs%20and%20market%20access%20simmered.%20I%20recall%20how%20in%202019%2C%20Trump's%20abrupt%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20benefits%20India%20enjoyed%20under%20the%20Generalized%20System%20of%20Preferences%20(GSP)%20dealt%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20relations.%20It%20highlighted%20his%20administration's%20tough%20stance%20on%20trade%20imbalances.%20I%20reckon%20under%20the%20current%20Trump%20rein%2C%20trade%20negotiations%20would%20likely%20remain%20contentious%2C%20with%20the%20US%20pushing%20for%20greater%20access%20to%20Indian%20markets%2C%20particularly%20in%20agriculture%2C%20dairy%2C%20and%20e-commerce%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20has%20every%20right%20to%20protect%20its%20domestic%20industries%20while%20expanding%20exports%20in%20sectors%20like%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20IT%20services%20and%20textiles.%20If%20Trump%20has%20based%20his%20foreign%20policy%20on%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20First%26quot%3B%2C%20Modi's%20doctrine%20is%20%26quot%3BMake%20in%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20Immigrants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20hardline%20stance%20on%20immigration%20is%20unsettling%20for%20many%20countries%2C%20including%20India.%20There%20are%20reports%20of%20India%20preparing%20to%20agree%20to%20take%20back%20under%2020%2C000%20of%20its%20undocumented%20citizens%20in%20the%20US.%20However%2C%20according%20to%202022%20official%20data%2C%20with%207%2C25%2C000%20illegal%20immigrants%2C%20India%20has%20the%20second-highest%20number%20of%20undocumented%20citizens%20in%20America%20after%20its%20neighbour%2C%20Mexico.%20Trump%20could%20demand%20that%20India%20accept%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20these%20citizens.%20His%20focus%20on%20this%20issue%20might%20intensify%2C%20especially%20given%20his%20previous%20emphasis%20on%20cracking%20down%20on%20immigration%20from%20non-European%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccepting%20large%20numbers%20of%20deportees%20would%20be%20politically%20sensitive%20in%20India.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20refusing%20or%20delaying%20cooperation%20might%20lead%20to%20strained%20relations%2C%20with%20Trump%20potentially%20leveraging%20other%20areas%2C%20like%20trade%20or%20visa%20policies%2C%20as%20bargaining%20chips.%20Big%20trouble%20is%20brewing%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrade%20And%20Trump's%20Zero-Tolerance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20bilateral%20trade%20in%20goods%20and%20services%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%20reached%20%24191.8%20billion%2C%20with%20India%20enjoying%20a%20trade%20surplus%20of%20%2445.7%20billion.%20Trump's%20administration%20will%20likely%20push%20hard%20to%20correct%20this%20imbalance%2C%20testing%20India's%20diplomatic%20and%20economic%20strategies.%20With%20the%20US%20being%20India's%20largest%20export%20market%2C%20how%20will%20New%20Delhi%20balance%20its%20interests%20and%20leverage%20its%20position%3F%20A%20tough%20call%20indeed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrade%20deficit%20in%20general%20is%20an%20irksome%20issue%20for%20Trump.%20The%20US%20trade%20deficit%20against%20India%2C%20though%20much%20less%20than%20that%20against%20China%2C%20remains%20a%20big%20worry%20for%20his%20administration.%20Trump%20after%20all%20had%20singled%20out%20Canada%20for%20their%20trade%20imbalance%20and%20threatened%20to%20make%20it%20America's%2051st%20state.%20Will%20he%20target%20India%20with%20higher%20tariffs%20or%20demand%20renegotiations%20of%20trade%20terms%3F%20In%20my%20view%2C%20Trump%20is%20likely%20to%20demand%20greater%20access%20to%20US%20goods%20and%20services%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20could%20face%20pressure%20to%20lower%20tariffs%20on%20several%20products%2C%20risking%20backlash%20from%20domestic%20industries%20that%20benefit%20from%20protectionist%20policies.%20Trump%20may%20also%20demand%20concessions%20on%20e-commerce%20regulations%2C%20data%20localisation%20requirements%20and%20government%20procurement%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWin%20Some%2C%20Lose%20Some%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%2C%20however%2C%20always%20room%20to%20manoeuvre%E2%80%94at%20least%20between%20Trump's%20%E2%80%98highway'%20and%20his%20%E2%80%98my%20way'.%20Take%20the%20H-1B%20visa%20programme%2C%20a%20lifeline%20for%20India's%20IT%20sector%20and%20a%20constant%20thorn%20in%20Trump's%20'America%20First'%20rhetoric.%20With%20Indians%20making%20up%20over%2070%25%20of%20H-1B%20recipients%2C%20any%20attempt%20to%20tighten%20eligibility%2C%20limit%20extensions%2C%20or%20increase%20fees%20would%20hit%20Indian%20professionals%20hard.%20Trump%20has%20never%20been%20shy%20about%20targeting%20H-1Bs%2C%20arguing%20they%20steal%20jobs%20from%20American%20workers.%20This%20time%2C%20his%20administration%20could%20be%20even%20more%20aggressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20are%20the%20students%E2%80%94over%20200%2C000%20Indians%20currently%20studying%20in%20the%20US%2C%20pumping%20billions%20into%20American%20universities.%20Trump%20might%20not%20explicitly%20go%20after%20them%2C%20but%20higher%20visa%20fees%2C%20post-study%20work%20restrictions%2C%20or%20broader%20immigration%20crackdowns%20could%20make%20life%20much%20harder.%20Of%20course%2C%20there's%20always%20the%20chance%20he%20may%20use%20them%20as%20bargaining%20chips%E2%80%94after%20all%2C%20everything's%20a%20deal%20in%20Trump's%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20could%20be%20India's%20play%3F%20Strategic%20autonomy%20must%20be%20preserved%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20in%20practice%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20may%20have%20to%20become%20more%20creative%2C%20agile%20and%20engaging.%20To%20start%20with%2C%20India's%20ambassador%20must%20be%20someone%20with%20contacts%20in%20the%20corridors%20of%20power%20and%20a%20person%20who%20can%20extensively%20promote%20India's%20interests.%20India%20could%20also%20leverage%20its%20Indo-Pacific%20importance%2C%20remind%20Washington%20that%20it%20remains%20a%20crucial%20counterweight%20to%20China%20and%E2%80%94let's%20be%20honest%E2%80%94make%20a%20few%20concessions.%20Opening%20up%20key%20sectors%20like%20retail%2C%20e-commerce%2C%20or%20defence%20to%20US%20firms%20might%20just%20buy%20India%20some%20breathing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20working%20the%20backchannels%E2%80%94Indian-origin%20officials%20in%20Trump's%20administration%2C%20pro-India%20lawmakers%2C%20corporate%20allies%E2%80%94might%20help%20soften%20the%20blows.%20India%20has%20a%20very%20delicate%20path%20to%20walk%20for%20the%20next%20four%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3ESyed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738156680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fob6ejgug_modi-trump-at-howdy-modi-event-_650x400_23_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-will-have-to-be-creative-with-trump-and-his-tariffs-7587969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20Trump%20has%20made%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20First%26quot%3B%20his%20battle%20cry%2C%20India%20has%20long%20sworn%20by%20its%20own%20foreign%20policy%20doctrine%3A%20strategic%20autonomy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brothers%20Kill%20Mother's%20Lover%20In%20Grisly%20Crime%2C%20Toss%20Intestines%20In%20Air%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20brothers%20allegedly%20stabbed%20their%20mother's%20lover%20to%20death%2C%20sliced%20his%20intestines%20and%20tossed%20them%20in%20the%20air%20in%20a%20grisly%20crime%20in%20Gujarat%20earlier%20this%20week.%20The%20two%20siblings%20had%20a%20resentment%20towards%20the%20victim%2C%20Ratanji%20Thakor%20(53)%2C%20as%20they%20believed%20that%20the%20victim's%20relationship%20with%20their%20mother%20%26quot%3Binsulted%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdishonoured%26quot%3B%20their%20dead%20father%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20Gujarat's%20Gandhinagar%20district%20on%20January%2026%20when%20the%20victim%2C%20a%20mason%20by%20profession%2C%20was%20building%20a%20house%20with%20his%20fellow%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20accused%20-%20Sanjay%20Thakor%20(27)%20and%20Jayesh%20Thakor%20(23)%20-%20attacked%20Ratanji%20with%20an%20iron%20rod%20in%20broad%20daylight.%20They%20then%20stabbed%20him%20in%20his%20stomach%20multiple%20times.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20the%20victim's%20intestines%20came%20out.%20But%20shockingly%2C%20the%20two%20men%20did%20not%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20took%20out%20the%20victim's%20intestines%2C%20tossed%20them%20into%20the%20air%2C%20and%20sliced%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20who%20witnessed%20the%20incident%20expressed%20massive%20disgust%20and%20shock.%20According%20to%20a%20senior%20official%2C%20some%20labourers%20tried%20to%20save%20the%20victim%20during%20the%20horrifying%20incident%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20a%20mason%20by%20profession%2C%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20the%20accused's%20mother%20since%20many%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20brothers%20disapproved%20of%20the%20relationship%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20were%20facing%20embarrassment%20in%20the%20family%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20victim's%20son%2C%20Ajay%2C%20who%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20accused%2C%20told%20the%20police%20that%20the%20two%20brothers%20had%20warned%20his%20father%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20their%20mother%20earlier.%20They%20even%20fought%20with%20the%20victim%20many%20times%2C%20he%20said.%20Following%20a%20dispute%2C%20the%20villagers%20also%20held%20a%20panchayat%20on%20the%20issue%20but%20did%20not%20find%20any%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20fled%20the%20scene%20on%20a%20bike%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20traced%20them%20down%20through%20a%20mobile%20location%20within%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20crime%20and%20arrested%20them.%20The%20weapons%20used%20in%20the%20murder%20have%20also%20been%20seized%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20accused%20for%20murder%20and%20inciting%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Mahendra%20Prasad)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3