%2C%20a%20volunteer%20with%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20who%20had%20a%20free%20run%20of%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20doctor%20had%20sought%20re-investigation%20and%20additional%20investigation%2C%20contending%20that%20others%20besides%20Sanjay%20Roy%20were%20involved.%20The%20conspirators%20and%20instigators%20have%20not%20been%20arrested%20and%20neither%20were%20those%20who%20saved%20and%20sheltered%20him%2C%20they%20had%20contended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20has%20allowed%20the%20parents%20to%20amend%20it%20and%20file%20a%20fresh%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2020%2C%20a%20Kolkata%20trial%20court%20awarded%20convict%20Sanjay%20Roy%20%26quot%3Blife%20term%20imprisonment%20till%20death%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%20post-graduate%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20found%20in%20the%20hospital's%20seminar%20room%20on%20August%209%20last%20year%2C%20following%20which%20the%20Kolkata%20police%20arrested%20civic%20volunteer%20Roy%20the%20next%20day%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20said%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20who%20returned%20to%20work%20after%2022.8.24%20should%20be%20regularised%20and%20their%20action%20will%20not%20be%20considered%20as%20absence%20from%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20its%20direction%20has%20been%20issued%20in%20view%20of%20specific%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20and%20so%20this%20will%20not%20be%20considered%20as%20a%20precedent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20deem%20it%20appropriate%20to%20clarify%20that%20if%20protesting%20workers%20had%20joined%20work%20post%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20then%20their%20absence%20shall%20be%20regularised%20and%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20absence%20from%20duty.%20This%20is%20issued%20in%20peculiar%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20of%20the%20cases%20and%20is%20not%20laying%20down%20any%20precedent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738151760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fob98l57o_rg-kar-protests_625x300_18_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-hear-petition-in-rg-kar-rape-murder-case-7587418%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20refused%20to%20consider%20a%20petition%20for%20re-investigation%20of%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20hospital%20that%20had%20shocked%20the%20nation%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-hear-petition-in-rg-kar-rape-murder-case-7587418%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20To%20Showcase%20Premium%20Cabin%20Product%2C%20Give%20Virtual%20Tour%20At%20Event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20will%20showcase%20its%20premium%20cabin%20product%20and%20in-flight%20offerings%20at%20Asia's%20most%20influential%20travel%20trade%20show%20to%20be%20held%20from%20January%2030%20to%20February%201%20at%20Mumbai's%20Jio%20World%20Convention%20Centre%2C%20the%20Tata-owned%20airline%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20inspiration%20from%20Air%20India's%20signature%20design%20philosophy%2C%20the%20exhibition%20booth%20at%20the%20Outbound%20Travel%20Mart%20(OTM)%20event%20has%20been%20conceptualised%20with%20'The%20Vista'%20as%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20its%20structure%2C%20blending%20aesthetics%20with%20immersive%20digital%20experiences%2C%20Air%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pavilion%20will%20showcase%20various%20aspects%20of%20Air%20India's%20transformation%20journey%2C%20captivating%20audiences%20with%20a%20live%20demonstration%20of%20business%20class%20and%20premium%20economy%20seats%20that%20are%20available%20on%20Air%20India's%20newly%20retrofitted%20A320%20family%20aircraft%2C%20the%20airline%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20aircraft%20come%20with%20subtle%20cabin%20mood%20lighting%2C%20spacious%20legroom%20and%20wider%20pitch%2C%20and%20modern%20features%20such%20as%20portable%20electronic%20device%20(PED)%20holders%20and%20USB%20ports%20to%20charge%20mobile%20phones%2C%20laptops%20and%20other%20gadgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisitors%20will%20be%20able%20to%20experience%20the%20seats%20in%20real-time%20while%20also%20getting%20a%20glimpse%20of%20Air%20India's%20brand%20new%20A350%20product%20at%20the%20virtual%20reality%20(VR)%20experience%20zone%2C%20Air%20India%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20will%20also%20display%20a%20selection%20of%20in-flight%20meals%20to%20showcase%20its%20refreshed%20menus%20and%20enhanced%20dining%20experience%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOTM%202025%20presents%20a%20significant%20platform%20for%20Air%20India%20to%20engage%20and%20deepen%20ties%20with%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20key%20trade%20visitors%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20while%20highlighting%20the%20milestones%20of%20our%20transformation%20journey.%20With%20the%20Air%20India%20pavilion%20featuring%20unique%20activations%20and%20immersive%20experiences%2C%20including%20our%20business%20class%20and%20premium%20economy%20seats%2C%20we%20are%20set%20to%20demonstrate%20our%20commitment%20to%20delivering%20world-class%20product%20and%20services%20to%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Air%20India%20chief%20commercial%20officer%20Nipun%20Aggarwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20VR%20experience%20zone%2C%20visitors%20can%20embark%20on%20a%20virtual%20journey%20of%20the%20A350%20aircraft%20that%20have%20recently%20been%20deployed%20between%20Delhi%20and%20London%20Heathrow%2C%20New%20York%20(JFK)%2C%20and%20Newark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India's%20A350%20aircraft%20feature%2028%20private%20suites%20in%20business%20class%20with%20full-flat%20beds%20in%20a%201-2-1%20configuration%2C%20and%20264%20spacious%20economy%20seats%20arranged%20in%20a%203-3-3%20configuration.%20Each%20suite%20in%20business%20class%20provides%20direct%20aisle%20access%2C%20sliding%20privacy%20doors%2C%20and%20a%20personal%20wardrobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20seats%20across%20cabins%20on%20the%20A350%20come%20with%20the%20latest-generation%20Panasonic%20eX3%20in-flight%20entertainment%20(IFE)%20system%20and%20HD%20screens%20that%20offer%20more%20than%203%2C800%20hours%20of%20entertainment%20content%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20Air%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20A350%20flights%20also%20feature%20the%20airline's%20new%20signature%20soft%20product%20and%20award-winning%20guest%20enhancements%2C%20including%20new%20chinaware%2C%20tableware%20and%20glassware%2C%20plush%20bedding%2C%20and%20bespoke%20amenity%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20India%20booth%20will%20also%20give%20visitors%20a%20chance%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20Maharaja%20Club%2C%20Air%20India's%20all-new%20frequent%20flyer%20programme%20that%20offers%20a%20host%20of%20privileges%20and%20exclusive%20benefits.%20In%20addition%2C%20visitors%20will%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20win%20multiple%20prizes%2C%20including%20curated%20gift%20hampers%20or%20a%20complimentary%20economy%20class%20ticket%2C%20through%20a%20raffle%20that%20will%20be%20conducted%20at%20the%20booth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20India%20group%20comprises%20full-service%20global%20airline%20Air%20India%20and%20low-cost%20regional%20carrier%20Air%20India%20Express.%20The%20Air%20India%20story%20began%20in%201932%20when%20JRD%20Tata%20piloted%20the%20airline's%20inaugural%20flight%20and%20opened%20the%20skies%20for%20aviation%20in%20India.%20Today%2C%20the%20Air%20India%20group%20employs%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20people%2C%20operates%20over%20300%20aircraft%20and%20carries%20customers%20to%2055%20domestic%20and%2048%20international%20destinations%20across%20five%20co