0a%20two-week%20break%20and%20was%20last%20seen%20leaving%20the%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Terminus%20station.%20When%20her%20family%20could%20not%20contact%20her%2C%20they%20filed%20a%20missing%20complaint%20and%20started%20looking%20for%20her%20in%20Mumbai.%20On%20January%2016%2C%20a%20decomposed%20body%20was%20recovered%20in%20Kanjurmarg%20and%20it%20was%20identified%20as%20Esther's.%20%26quot%3BWe%20looked%20for%20my%20daughter%20after%20she%20went%20missing.%20Finally%2C%20after%2010%20days%2C%20her%20body%20was%20recovered.%20No%20parent%20should%20face%20the%20kind%20of%20trauma%20I%20have%20faced%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Prasad%20told%20NDTV%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20eyewitnesses%20and%20the%20only%20clue%20police%20had%20was%20footage%20from%20a%20CCTV%20camera%20at%20the%20railway%20station.%20The%20footage%20showed%20a%20man%20with%20a%20moustache%20carrying%20Esther's%20bag%20and%20walking%20with%20her.%20A%20porter%20at%20the%20station%20identified%20him%20as%20Sanap.%20He%20was%20arrested%20in%20Nashik%20on%20March%203%20and%20charged%20with%20raping%20and%20murdering%20Esther.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Police%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20based%20largely%20on%20circumstantial%20evidence.%20According%20to%20police%2C%20Sanap%20pretended%20to%20be%20a%20cab%20driver%20when%20he%20spotted%20Esther%20at%20the%20station%20on%20the%20winter%20morning.%20He%20offered%20to%20drive%20her%20to%20the%20south%20Mumbai%20hostel%20where%20she%20stayed.%20But%20on%20exiting%20the%20station%2C%20Esther%20saw%20Sanap%20did%20not%20have%20a%20cab%2C%20but%20a%20bike.%20Police%20said%20Sanap%20somehow%20managed%20to%20convince%20Esther%20to%20sit%20pillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20way%2C%20he%20stopped%20on%20a%20service%20road%20on%20the%20Eastern%20Express%20Highway%20near%20Kanjurmarg%20on%20the%20pretext%20that%20the%20bike%20had%20run%20out%20of%20petrol.%C2%A0According%20to%20police%2C%20he%20dragged%20Esther%20into%20bushes%20nearby%20and%20tried%20to%20rape%20her.%20When%20she%20resisted%2C%20he%20hit%20her%20head%20on%20a%20stone%20many%20times%20and%20strangled%20her%20with%20her%20dupatta.%20Sanap%20then%20tried%20to%20burn%20Esther's%20body%20in%20the%20thick%20bushes%20and%20escaped%20with%20her%20suitcase%2C%20which%20had%20her%20laptop%20and%20other%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Conviction%2C%20And%20The%20Acquittal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202015%2C%20a%20Mumbai%20court%20convicted%20Sanap%20of%20Esther's%20rape%20and%20murder%20and%20sentenced%20him%20to%20death.%20Awarding%20the%20sentence%2C%20special%20judge%20Vrushali%20Joshi%20said%20it%20was%20a%20rarest-of-the-rare%20case%20and%20qualified%20for%20the%20death%20penalty.%20%26quot%3BThe%20case%20falls%20under%20the%20category%20of%20the%20rarest%20of%20rare%2C%20hence%20the%20accused%20is%20awarded%20the%20death%20sentence.%20He%20must%20be%20hanged%20by%20his%20neck%20till%20he%20is%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20judge.%20The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20subsequently%20upheld%20the%20death%20penalty.%20The%20high%20court%20said%20such%20a%20person%20would%20remain%20a%20menace%20to%20society%20and%20that%20the%20crime%20warranted%20the%20death%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20yesterday%20ruled%20that%20the%20prosecution's%20evidence%20was%20inadequate%20to%20sustain%20the%20conviction.%20The%20facts%20of%20the%20case%2C%20it%20said%2C%20compel%20the%20court%20to%20conclude%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20gaping%20holes%20in%20the%20prosecution%20story%20leading%20to%20the%20irresistible%20conclusion%20that%20there%20is%20something%20more%20than%20what%20meets%20the%20eye%20in%20this%20case.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20old%20adage%2C%20witness%20may%20lie%20but%20not%20the%20circumstances%2C%20may%20be%20correct%2C%20however%2C%20the%20circumstances%20adduced%2C%20as%20held%20by%20this%20Court%2C%20should%20be%20fully%20established.%20There%20is%20a%20legal%20distinction%20between%20'may%20be%20proved'%20and%20'must%20be%20or%20should%20be%20proved'%20as%20held%20by%20this%20Court.%20The%20circumstances%20relied%20upon%20when%20stitched%20together%20do%20not%20lead%20to%20the%20sole%20hypothesis%20of%20the%20guilt%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20we%20do%20not%20find%20that%20the%20chain%20is%20so%20complete%20as%20not%20to%20leave%20any%20reasonable%20ground%20for%20the%20conclusion%20consistent%20with%20the%20innocence%20of%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20Justice%20Prashant%20Kumar%20Mishra%20and%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20Leave%20It%20To%20God%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20Machilipatnam%20home%2C%20Mr%20Prasad%20said%20he%20had%20heard%20about%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20but%20he%20could%20do%20nothing%20about%20it.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20we%20do%3F%20We%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20what%20was%20happening.%20We%20also%20do%20not%20know%20that%20he%20(Sanap)%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20But%20what%20shall%20we%20do%3F%20I%20leave%20it%20to%20God%20and%20whatever%20happens%2C%20I%20will%20not%20be%20getting%20my%20daughter%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elderly%20man%20said%20the%20death%20penalty%20had%20given%20him%20some%20closure.%20%26quot%3BWe%20appreciated%20that%20some%20justice%20was%20done.%20Now%20that%20has%20completely%20changed.%20I%20do%20not%20know%20the%20reasons.%20Again%2C%20I%20recollect%20my%20sorrowful%20days%2010%20years%20back%2C%20how%20I%20suffered%20in%20Mumbai%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0Mr%20Prasad%20said%20police%20had%20collected%20ample%20evidence%20and%20arrested%20the%20right%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20would%20pursue%20the%20case%20further%20and%20file%20a%20review%20petition%20in%20the%20top%20court%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20sir%2C%20I%20cannot%20do%20that.%20The%20problem%20is%20I%20am%2070%20plus.%20It%20is%20very%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20move%20from%20my%20place.%20I%20am%20a%20retired%20man%20and%20my%20wife%20is%20not%20well%2C%20she%20is%20a%20diabetic.%20So%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20can%20approach%20at%20this%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738149720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-10%2Ftcs-techie_650x400_61446190210.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Festher-anuhya-rape-murder-case-techies-2014-rape-murder-acquittal-10-years-later-and-a-helpless-father-7586711%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22S%20Jonathan%20Prasad%20lived%20a%20nightmare%2011%20years%20back%20after%20his%2023-year-old%20daughter%20Esther%20Anuhya's%20rotten%20body%20was%20found%20on%20a%20Mumbai%20road%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Festher-anuhya-rape-murder-case-techies-2014-rape-murder-acquittal-10-years-later-and-a-helpless-father-7586711%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'He%20was%20yaaron%20ka%20yaar'%3A%20Virat%20Kohli's%20teammates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738149626000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117685774%2Cimgsize-45244.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fhe-was-yaaron-ka-yaar-virat-kohlis-teammates-recall-the-last-time-he-played-in-ranji-trophy%2Farticleshow%2F117685038.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli's%20highly%20anticipated%20return%20to%20domestic%20cricket%20after%20over%2012%20years%20has%20created%20excitement%20at%20Delhi's%20Arun%20Jaitley%20Stadium.%20Reuniting%20with%20former%20teammates%2C%20Kohli's%20presence%20offers%20a%20valuable%20learning%20experience%20for%20young%20players.%20His%20dedication%20to%20the%20game%20and%20team-first%20mentality%20are%2