a%20new%20version%20of%20its%20AI%20model%2C%20Qwen2.5%20Max%2C%20claiming%20it%20performed%20better%20than%20DeepSeek's%20AI%2C%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4o%20and%20Meta's%20Llama.%20The%20Chinese%20tech%20company's%20cloud%20division%20claimed%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Falibaba-releases-ai-model-it-claims-surpasses-deepseek-v3-2025-01-29%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3BQwen%202.5-Max%20outperforms%20...%20almost%20across%20the%20board%20GPT-4o%2C%20DeepSeek-V3%20and%20Llama-3.1-405B%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20the%20advanced%20open-source%20AI%20models%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20shockwaves%20DeepSeek's%20AI%20models%20have%20sent%20in%20the%20global%20AI%20landscape.%20The%20release%20of%20DeepSeek's%20AI%20assistant%2C%20powered%20by%20the%20DeepSeek-V3%20model%20on%20January%2010%2C%20and%20its%20R1%20model%20on%20January%2020%2C%20rattled%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20causing%20tech%20stocks%20to%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek-V3%2C%20which%20it%20says%20is%20as%20good%20as%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4o%20but%20much%20cheaper.%20Alibaba's%20introduction%20of%20Qwen%202.5%20Max%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20direct%20response%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20DeepSeek%2C%20which%20recently%20released%20another%20model%2C%20R1%2C%20causing%20a%20stir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%2C%20founded%20just%2020%20months%20ago%20in%20Hangzhou%2C%20Alibaba's%20home%20city%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20field%20of%20AI%2C%20drawing%20attention%20for%20its%20low-cost%2C%20high-performance%20models.%20The%20startup%20has%20forced%20established%20players%20like%20Alibaba%2C%20Tencent%2C%20and%20Baidu%20to%20enhance%20their%20AI%20systems%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20AI