istan%2C%20Key%20Projects%20Hit%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20temporarily%20suspended%20foreign%20assistance%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20re-evaluation%20following%20an%20executive%20order%20issued%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20according%20to%20a%20media%20report%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20has%20instantly%20stopped%20a%20number%20of%20important%20United%20States%20Agency%20For%20International%20Development%20(USAID)%20projects%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20including%20the%20Ambassadors%20Fund%20for%20Cultural%20Preservation%20(AFCP)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20flagship%20programme%20to%20promote%20cultural%20heritage%20preservation%20and%20protection%2C%20the%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20embassy%20here%2C%20the%20AFCP%20fund%20%26quot%3Bhelps%20protect%20historic%20buildings%2C%20archaeological%20sites%2C%20museum%20collections%2C%20and%20traditional%20cultural%20expressions%20like%20indigenous%20languages%20and%20crafts%20around%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20an%20unnamed%20official%20at%20the%20US%20Consulate%20in%20Karachi%2C%20the%20report%20said%20the%20US%20has%20paused%20Pakistan's%20foreign%20assistance%20for%20re-evaluation%20as%20per%20the%20executive%20order%20issued%20by%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20projects%20related%20to%20the%20energy%20sector%20have%20also%20come%20to%20a%20halt%20as%20a%20result%20of%20this%20decision%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20Power%20Sector%20Improvement%20Activity%2C%20Pakistan%20Private%20Sector%20Energy%20Activity%2C%20Energy%20Sector%20Advisory%20Services%20Project%2C%20Clean%20Energy%20Loan%20Portfolio%20Guarantee%20Program%20and%20Pakistan%20Climate%20Financing%20Activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomic%20growth-related%20four%20projects%20have%20also%20been%20hit.%20Among%20them%2C%20Social%20Protection%20Activity%20was%20the%20only%20programme%20supposed%20to%20end%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20move%20also%20hit%20many%20projects%20related%20to%20health%2C%20agriculture%2C%20livelihood%20and%20food%20security%2C%20flood%2C%20climate%2C%20and%20education.%20Democracy%2C%20Human%20Rights%2C%20and%20Governance%20funds%20are%20also%20hit%20by%20Trump's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFears%20are%20being%20expressed%20that%20some%20of%20these%20programmes%20will%20be%20shelved%20forever%20or%20at%20least%20reduced%20significantly%2C%20according%20to%20Geo%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20total%20value%20of%20the%20affected%20projects%20is%20not%20known%2C%20as%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20how%20much%20annual%20aid%20the%20US%20is%20currently%20pumping%20into%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20officials%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20not%20confirmed%20the%20development%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20Trump's%20executive%20measures%20on%20assistance%20stoppage%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20without%20naming%20any%20country%2C%20Tammy%20Bruce%2C%20spokesman%20for%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20State%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BConsistent%20with%20President%20Trump's%20Executive%20Order%20on%20Reevaluating%20and%20Realigning%20United%20States%20Foreign%20Aid%2C%20Secretary%20Rubio%20has%20paused%20all%20US%20foreign%20assistance%20funded%20by%20or%20through%20the%20State%20Department%20and%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20(USAID)%20for%20review.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAs%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20has%20said%2C%20'Every%20dollar%20we%20spend%2C%20every%20programme%20we%20fund%2C%20and%20every%20policy%20we%20pursue%20must%20be%20justified%20with%20the%20answer%20to%20three%20simple%20questions%3A%20Does%20it%20make%20America%20safer%3F%20Does%20it%20make%20America%20stronger%3F%20Does%20it%20make%20America%20more%20prosperous%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20