l%2Fshots-fired-in-air-to-celebrate-toll-plaza-contract-in-madhya-pradesh%2Farticleshow%2F117679612.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMockery%26quot%3B%3A%20Opposition%20MPs%20In%20Waqf%20House%20Panel%20Say%20Their%20Suggestions%20Ignored%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOpposition%20MPs%20on%20the%20House%20panel%20examining%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20have%20alleged%20that%20BJP%20members%20on%20the%20committee%20ignored%20their%20objections%20and%20that%20the%20recommendations%20made%20in%20the%20report%20are%20not%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20MPs%20alleged%20that%20they%20received%20the%20655-page%20report%20last%20evening%20and%20hardly%20had%20time%20to%20study%20it%20and%20make%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20today%20adopted%20the%20draft%20report%20after%20a%2016-11%20majority%20vote.%20The%20report%20will%20be%20presented%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20tomorrow.%20Opposition%20MPs%20have%20submitted%20their%20dissent%20notes%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel's%20chairperson%20and%20veteran%20BJP%20leader%20Jagdambika%20Pal%20said%20several%20amendments%20approved%20by%20the%20committee%20addressed%20the%20concerns%20of%20Opposition%20members.%20He%20said%20the%20proposed%20law%20will%20help%20Waqf%20boards%20function%20more%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20Bill%20would%20be%20re-introduced%20in%20Parliament%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Budget%20Session%2C%20Mr%20Pal%20said%20that's%20for%20the%20Speaker%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20MPs%20on%20the%20panel%2C%20however%2C%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20proposed%20law%20would%20destroy%20Waqf%20boards%20and%20lead%20to%20government%20interference%20in%20its%20functioning.%20Reports%20said%2066%20amendments%20were%20proposed%20--%2023%20by%20BJP%20MPs%20and%2044%20from%20the%20Opposition.%20MPs%20from%