26quot%3Bwholly%20perverse%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BStatements%20of%20the%20victims%20have%20not%20been%20taken%20into%20consideration.%20What%20we%20said%20during%20the%20deliberations%20has%20not%20been%20taken%20into%20consideration.%20The%20question%20that%20arises%20is%2C%20the%20stakeholders'%20view%20which%20we%20have%20expressed%2C%20why%20it%20did%20not%20appeal%20to%20the%20chairman%3F%20JPC%20proceedings%20have%20turned%20into%20mockery.%20All%20other%20views%20have%20been%20ignored%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MP%20Arvind%20Sawant%20said%20the%20proposed%20amendments%20are%20against%20the%20Constitution.%20%26quot%3BUntil%20yesterday%2C%20people%20used%20to%20come%20through%20elections%20in%20Waqf%2C%20but%20now%20you%20are%20removing%20elections.%20People%20will%20be%20nominated%20there%2C%20and%20the%20central%20government%20will%20do%20it.%20Today%2C%20there%20is%20a%20provision%20to%20bring%20non-Muslims%20into%20Waqf%2C%20so%20tomorrow%20they%20might%20do%20the%20same%20in%20our%20temples%20because%20the%20issue%20of%20equality%20will%20come%20up%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sawant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20objections%20and%20suggestions%20were%20made%20which%20have%20not%20been%20included%20in%20this%20report.%20The%20government%20has%20made%20the%20report%20as%20per%20them.%20Unconstitutional%20amendments%20have%20been%20brought%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20minorities%20have%20been%20harmed.%20The%20amendments%20have%20been%20brought%20to%20single%20out%20the%20minorities%2C%20especially%20the%20Muslim%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20House%20panel%20on%20August%208%20after%20Union%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20introduced%20it%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738140540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Frjki9k0g_waqf-panel_625x