c-waste-textile-waste%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What%20An%20Indian%20'Thali'%20Can%20Tell%20Us%20About%20DeepSeek%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhy%20are%20US%20stock%20markets%20recovering%20a%20bit%20after%20a%20day%20of%20bloodbath%20linked%20to%20China's%20AI%20wonder%2C%20DeepSeek%3F%20To%20understand%20the%20question%2C%20we%20need%20to%20do%20some%20deep-seeking%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20intricate%20interplay%20between%20technological%20wonders%2C%20economic%20behaviour%20and%20stock%20market%20movements.%20But%2C%20first%20up%2C%20something%20about%20India's%20%3Cem%3Ethali%20%3C%2Fem%3Emeals%E2%80%94they%20can%20tell%20us%20something%20about%20the%20open-source-based%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20(AGI)%20engine%20that%20has%20set%20tongues%20wagging%20as%20it%20rivals%20ChatGPT%20and%20Gemini%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20development%20costs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20you%20can%20buy%20a%20cheap%20%3Cem%3Ethali%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20a%20roadside%20stall%20that%20serves%20a%20wholesome%20meal%20at%20Rs%2050%20a%20plate%2C%20or%20go%20for%20a%20lavish%20unlimited%20%3Cem%3Ethali%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20for%20Rs%201%2C500.%20There%20are%20differences%20in%20their%20features%2C%20style%2C%20and%20details.%20At%20the%20roadside%20stall%2C%20you%20may%20get%20a%20small%20thermocol%20plate%20with%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20dishes%20to%20go%20with%20the%20main%20course%20rice%2C%20while%20liveried%20waiters%20will%20fawn%20on%20you%20with%20silver%20cutlery%20in%20an%20air-conditioned%20environment%20when%20you%20order%20a%20thali%20at%20a%20five-star%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeepSeek%20Is%20Food%20For%20Thought%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20Chinese-backed%20hedge%20fund%2C%20High-Flyer%2C%20has%20given%20us%20through%20DeepSeek%20is%20like%20a%20decent%2C%20affordable%20%3Cem%3Ethali%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20based%20on%20open-source%20technology%20that%20allows%20people%20to%20tweak%20its%20features%2C%20much%20like%20a%20%3Cem%3Ethali%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20allows%20a%20second%20helping%20after%20a%20plate%20is%20served.%20It%20is%20based%20on%20limited%20specifications%2C%20but%20it%20also%20cleverly%20circumvents%20some%20advanced%2C%20ambitious%20features%2C%20and%20matches%20up%20to%20in-vogue%20engines%20such%20as%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20is%20food%20for%20thought%2C%20even%20in%20literal%20terms%2C%20as%20it%20does%20the%20work%20of%20a%20human%20brain.%20Its%20R1%20engine%20built%20at%20an%20estimated%20cost%20of%20only%20%245.6%20million%20by%20a%20one-year-old%20startup%20that%20matches%20ChatGPT%20offers%20a%20lesson%20in%20utilitarian%20economics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20easier%20way%20to%20understand%20the%20phenomenon%20is%20to%20compare%20DeepSeek%20with%20a%20Chinese-made%20Android%20phone%20equipped%20with%20features%20quite%20comparable%20to%20an%20iPhone%20that%20runs%20on%20Apple's%20proprietary%20iOS.%20By%20developing%20Android%20as%20an%20easily%20usable%20mobile%20OS%20platform%2C%20Google%20gave%20the%20world's%20phonemakers%20a%20cheaper%20alternative%20to%20iOS.%20DeepSeek%20seems%20to%20be%20returning%20the%20favour%20with%20a%20cut-rate%20AI%20engine%20that%20may%20help%20proliferate%20the%20use%20of%20AGI%2C%20much%20like%20how%20Asians%20seized%20on%20Android%20while%20the%20US-centric%20iPhone%20got%20blissfully%20isolated%20in%20its%20elite%2C%20high-profit%20ecosystem.%20Another%20way%20to%20look%20at%20DeepSeek%20is%20to%20see%20it%20as%20an%20equivalent%20of%20the%20open-source%20Linux%20OS%20platform%20that%20challenged%20Windows%20in%20its%20prime.%20Windows%20survived%20and%20grew%20with%20its%20own%20strategy%2C%20but%20Linux%20changed%20the%20way%20the%20industry%20behaves.%20It%20is%20still%20a%20great%20technological%20force%20behind%20the%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeepSeek%20Challenges%20'Core'%20Players%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstandably%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20called%20DeepSeek's%20arrival%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20American%20giants.%20I%20want%20to%20call%20DeepSeek%20the%20Android%20of%20AI%20for%20its%20potential%20power%20to%20proliferate%20its%20use%20and%20challenge%20established%20technology%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20point%20is%20that%20AGI%2C%20which%20learns%20things%20and%20articulates%20expressions%20like%20humans%2C%20needs%20a%20humongous%20amount%20of%20processing%20power%2C%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20consumes%20tonnes%20of%20electricity%20to%20make%20the%20volumes%20of%20data%20come%20together%20in%20a%20cohesive%20form.%20AI%20needs%20a%20lot%20of%20%26quot%3Btraining%26quot%3B%3B%20it%20is%20helped%20by%20advanced%20GPUs%20(graphic%20processing%20units)%20for%20high-speed%20mathematical%20calculations%20that%20power%20up%20machine%20learning.%20Nvidia%2C%20once%20a%20leader%20in%20humbler%20graphics%20cards%20that%20enhanced%20the%20video%20or%20gaming%20experience%20on%20your%20PC%2C%20is%20today%20a%20leader%20in%20AI%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20GPU%20clout%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20its%20stock%20grow%2020%20times%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Nvidia%20Wipeout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20Nvidia's%20stock%20fell%2017%25%E2%80%94nearly%20%24600%20billion%E2%80%94in%20history's%20biggest%20single-day%20wipeout%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20jury%20is%20out%20on%20whether%20various%20US%20plans%20to%20invest%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20AI-linked%20ventures%20is%20a%20smart%20move.%20Nvidia's%20computing%20power%20is%20undeniable%2C%20but%20what%20DeepSeek%20is%20proving%20is%20that%20you%20can%20build%20a%20good-enough%20monster%20without%20necessarily%20having%20the%20best-in-class%20GPUs.%20Its%20training%20methods%20also%20differ.%20Picture%20it%20like%20a%20dog-whisperer%20who%20can%20tame%20pets%20at%20cheaper%20rates%20to%20do%20smarter%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20has%20recovered%20somewhat%20after%20the%20Monday%20mayhem%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20cited%20for%20it%20is%20the%20end-user%20perspective%20on%20AI.%20Just%20like%20you%20can%20buy%20a%20cheaper%20%3Cem%3Ethali%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20an%20Android%20phone%2C%20DeepSeek%20can%20make%20companies%20embrace%20Generative%20AI%20that%20can%20create%20content%20at%20more%20affordable%20budgets.%20And%20that%20is%20good%20for%20their%20bottom%20lines.%20As%20investment%20bank%20UBS%20noted%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20DeepSeek%20implies%20that%20AI%20applications%20and%20the%20intelligence%20layer%20that%20goes%20with%20them%20will%20gain%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20enabling%20layer%20(GPU%20power)%20in%20terms%20of%20cost%20advantage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina's%20Clever%20Timing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20the%20US%20still%20retains%20its%20leadership%20as%20the%20creator%20of%20core%20technologies%20that%20power%20the%20AI%20revolution.%20But%20the%20timing%20of%20DeepSeek's%20release%20is%20such%20that%20President%20Trump%20may%20think%20twice%20about%20slapping%20trade%20restrictions%20on%20China%20in%20some%20spheres%2C%20while%20investors%20all%20set%20to%20bet%20their%20farms%20on%20American%20AI%20may%20ponder%20on%20the%20most%20optimal%20way%20to%20spread%20their%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%2C%20as%20an%20across-the-board%20phenomenon%2C%20is%20headed%20for%20interesting%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Madhavan%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20senior%20editor%2C%20writer%20and%20columnist%20with%20more%20than%2030%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20having%20worked%20for%20Reuters%2C%20The%20Economic%20Times%2C%20Business%20Standard%20and%20Hindustan%20Times%20after%20starting%20out%20in%20the%20Times%20of%20India%20Group.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C