%20company%20and%20reach%20potential%20buyers%2C%20the%20founder%20leveraged%20digital%20platforms%20like%20IndiaMart%2C%20Justdial%2C%20and%20Exporter%20India.%20These%20platforms%20helped%20him%20connect%20with%20the%20right%20customers%20and%20expand%20his%20reach%20far%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20made%20600-700%20calls%20every%20month%2C%20and%20sometimes%20it%20took%20up%20to%20three%20months%20to%20convert%20a%20lead%20into%20a%20customer.%20But%20we%20remained%20consistent%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20made%20all%20the%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suhail%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20battling%20the%20early%20struggles%20with%20a%20well-planned%20strategy%2C%20Athar%20Packaging%20Solutions%20has%20been%20able%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20clients%2C%20including%20companies%20like%20Khadi%20Natural%2C%20Gopala%20Fresh%2C%20and%20Sai%20Expo%20Mart%2C%20as%20well%20as%20smaller%20businesses%20and%20self-help%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20our%20customers%2C%20Khadi%20Natural%2C%20started%20with%2010%2C000%20pouches%20in%20the%20pilot%20phase%2C%20and%20now%20they%E2%80%99re%20ordering%20over%201%2C00%2C000%20pouches.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20trust%20we%E2%80%99ve%20built%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20shares%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F373638%2Fyash-pakka-ltd-ved-krishna-chuk-compostable-packaging-sustainable-products%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwitching%20to%20sustainable%20packaging%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20primarily%20driven%20by%20our%20commitment%20to%20environmental%20responsibility%20and%20the%20growing%20consumer%20demand%20for%20eco-friendly%20products.%20We%20believe%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20minimise%20our%20ecological%20footprint%20and%20contribute%20positively%20to%20the%20planet.%20As%20for%20the%20quali